{"tid":1996254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那27歲醫生放狗疑被狗繩絆倒　因血友病流血不止　顱內出血嚴重慘死","createTime":"2020-04-30T23:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:48:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"698f99b5aa23e698ca776d056b721f0dc75a84cb","tid":1996254,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:27:55.000Z","msg":"內地一名男子帶愛犬出街遛狗，想不到發生恐怖意外。四川一名27歲男醫生日前帶愛犬出街散步，途中疑不慎被狗繩絆倒，倒地頭部受傷，流血不止當場昏迷，送院後不治，狗狗嚇得瑟縮一旁。院方指傷者患血友病，顱內出血嚴重致搶救無效，家屬決定將他有用的器官捐出，讓他遺愛人間幫助更多人。<br />\n<br />\n4月26日下午3時，四川南充市嘉陵江邊，一名27歲黃衣男子帶着一隻掛上狗繩的阿拉斯加雪橇犬散步，行到江四橋橋下時，疑被手牽着的狗繩絆倒，倒地後流血不止，當地昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n網傳影片所見，男子的愛犬是阿拉斯加雪橇犬，出事後被綁在附近的燈柱上，身旁有血迹，在案發現場呆呆站着，一旁樓梯底有一大灘血。男子被送到醫院搶救，但傷勢嚴重最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n內媒記者向該院查詢，得悉死者是一名醫生，送院後情況極不樂觀，因為患有血友病，送院時顱內出血嚴重，盡力搶救可惜回天乏術。醫護人員向家屬交代情況後，家人決定將他有用的器官捐出，希望他仍能幫助更多人。<br />\n<br />\n網民對醫生的死感惋惜，但卻有人稱不明白事主為何患血有病還去放狗，又質疑醫生應該知道風險，亦有網民擔心他遺下愛犬的安危。<br />\n<br />\n血友病是一種遺傳性疾病，會令人體無法凝血結成血塊止血，病人受傷後流血時間更長，容易關節積血、腦出血等，萬一內臟出血或顱內出血易危及生命，患者又被稱為「玻璃人」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200430/332615239864553472.jpeg/_kgOaakP3mkx6r_1RRiv82HxIv7PeAElkmEmNJJhJjQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200430%2F332615239864553472.jpeg%2F_kgOaakP3mkx6r_1RRiv82HxIv7PeAElkmEmNJJhJjQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=96c76b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200430/332615502058885120.jpeg/g_GBybJnfC6ySgHQEp5KoDerET1s6TsgUicKVVInClU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200430%2F332615502058885120.jpeg%2Fg_GBybJnfC6ySgHQEp5KoDerET1s6TsgUicKVVInClU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=5bf3b2ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b8e4e796a9038dd0aeb19e92241e328b43f2da1","tid":1996254,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29423454cc7b1193e80b0c944ebe5f5a0ee58e3d","tid":1996254,"uid":272355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"對準政權<br />\n完"},{"pid":"517515e0e6eef4284698c5cb04de6eeb6a87d4b2","tid":1996254,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b8e4e796a9038dd0aeb19e92241e328b43f2da1","tid":1996254,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:32:15.000Z","msg":"係咪要告隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dee28c9574ce4c81df438a0ce52bfdcdb159f1","tid":1996254,"uid":193792,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:37:35.000Z","msg":"隻狗應該好大心理陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行行下街主人突然間出血無氣"},{"pid":"6543eb9ad39eb7fedafa6b119d7ec82d0882123a","tid":1996254,"uid":258513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"比較擔心狗狗下場多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7894da000f8a3111750518bd17ce99c4a242bc","tid":1996254,"uid":83759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6543eb9ad39eb7fedafa6b119d7ec82d0882123a","tid":1996254,"uid":258513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"比較擔心狗狗下場多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"屋企人唔要<br />\n最終變左狗肉"},{"pid":"d851a3d5d63fb52108c572308cee8b7f0880accc","tid":1996254,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:15:43.000Z","msg":"咁啲器官仲捐得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e085fbff695ab63b8abdad301c56eb74b1334765"